===Noun===
'''thaw'''

# The melting of ice, snow, or other [[congeal]]ed matter; the resolution of ice, or the like, into the state of a fluid; liquefaction by heat of anything congealed by frost; also, a warmth of weather sufficient to melt that which is congealed. —[[w:Dryden]].

